lead_paragraph: The Italian Grand Prix will stay on the Formula One calendar at Monza for at least three more years but a deal has yet to be signed, the sport's commercial supremo Bernie Ecclestone said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Monza Deal Agreed but Not Signed, Says Ecclestone
headline.main: Monza Deal Agreed but Not Signed, Says Ecclestone
